[SN]TITLE[SN]
The kids speaking Welsh at school

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Some of you might learn different languages at school - but did you know there are schools in Wales where Welsh is spoken as the main language?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 July 2017 Last updated at 07:16 BST
Well now the Welsh government have said they want more people to be able to speak the language.
We sent Ricky to one of those schools to find out more.
